videoSnippet.title: Never Play The French! | Isle of Man (2018)

Vidit Gujrathi Santosh vs Debashis Das
Isle of Man Open Tournament
22 Oct 2018.
French Defense: Rubinstein, Fort Knox Variation (C10)

1. e4 e6 2. d4 d5 3. Nc3 dxe4 4. Nxe4 Bd7 5. Nf3 Bc6 6. Bd3 Nd7 7. O-O Ngf6 8. Ng3 Be7 9. c4 O-O 10. Bf4 b6 11. Qe2 Bb7 12. Rad1 Re8 13. Bc2 Qc8 14. Ba4 Bf8 15. Ne5 c6 16. Rd3 a6 17. Rc1 Ra7 18. a3 Qa8 19. Ne4 b5 20. Bc2 c5 21. Ng5 bxc4 22. Rg3 g6 23. Nxh7 Nxh7 24. Bxg6 Ndf6 25. Qh5
